{"tid":1652994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係太潔癖","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:17:46.000Z","uid":2719,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"423b195819eba63d671124d8974c4f7d3b51c055","tid":1652994,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:49:21.000Z","msg":"依家其實可以文宣香港已戒嚴，6/9/10點關黨鐵，港共可以話修復工程，但又點解釋放狗巡又亂拉岀夜街嘅人？<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係太潔癖，無論係鶳定官方認證方面。明明行緊宵禁，港共無宣布就唔係；明明話還眼還命斷手斷腳，就大叫夠啦唔好打死人啦。好啦如果你話嗰時左膠唔係同路人，又有無諗過點解決？有人話打埋、拉開，用更大聲講咩事蓋過左膠把聲，但點解無人理？咁同默許有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n我開過post講過，示人我地係v煞/Batman，但內裡一定要保留joker嘅血。裝方面狗已經係Batman，現實又無v煞咁強嘅人類。係咁嘅情況下，如果連joker嘅心都無邊夠做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6WdGYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6WdGYU.jpg&h=ede32701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攝影師影呢張相代表啲乜？<br />\n佢呢個作品代表佢咩立場？諗下 考慮下"},{"pid":"8118a43ded81eee85d5d149a43981eaac0d2df2f","tid":1652994,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"554a7fd7652f76b02752c4249d9acc4191269e3c","tid":1652994,"uid":167883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1652695/page/1\" /><br />\nBTW聽唔明"},{"pid":"ec837dae0f632f75348b24c5b097986326f62453","tid":1652994,"uid":306966,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"554a7fd7652f76b02752c4249d9acc4191269e3c","tid":1652994,"uid":167883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1652695/page/1\" /><br />\nBTW聽唔明"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"簡單講 唔好玩玩下 囉條命出黎先贏"},{"pid":"19e1d0178f5a42e9f29537357edf6e5a290484c9","tid":1652994,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec837dae0f632f75348b24c5b097986326f62453","tid":1652994,"uid":306966,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"554a7fd7652f76b02752c4249d9acc4191269e